      • Staging

        public Staging(java.lang.String command,
       java.lang.String buildpackUrl,
       java.lang.String stack,
       java.lang.Integer healthCheckTimeout)
        参数:
        command - the application command; may be null
        buildpackUrl - a custom buildpack url (e.g. https://github.com/cloudfoundry/java-buildpack.git); may be null
        stack - the stack to use when staging the application; may be null
        healthCheckTimeout - the amount of time the platform should wait when verifying that an app started; may be null
